OL,5, Protections for NHS staff to speak out 
OL,6, about wrongdoing may be insufficient to
OL,7, prevent another big scandal like that  
OL,8, at the Mid Staffordshire hospital      
OL,9, trust, an expert has told BBC News.    
OL,11,FSir Robert Francis led the inquiry into
OL,12,Fhundreds of patient deaths at Stafford 
OL,13,FHospital more than a decade ago.       
OL,15,FHe says despite subsequent attempts to 
OL,16,Fencourage whistleblowing, some still   
OL,17,Fpay a heavy price for speaking up.     
OL,19,FAnd this victimisation discourages     
OL,20,Fothers from coming forward.            
